        <mxCell id="OtxXyDLVaMyX7tXUTaGo-80" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Logical Recombination&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;CEMENTO makes it easier to declare logical combinations (AND, OR) by separating the operator from the restriction branches. Users can &quot;nest&quot; or bridge several restrictions together in a manner consistent with the streams analogy.&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
