        <mxCell id="vY-UiPPvd2R0Yn6vORtP-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Nested Collections&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;CEMENTO allows the use of the native &lt;b&gt;List&lt;/b&gt; object for defining collections. Collections can also be nested within other collections at increasing complexity.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Collections are used to define common OWL constructs. CEMENTO supports: owl:intersectionOf, owl:unionOf, owl:oneOf, owl:complementOf, and&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: center; background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;owl:datatypeComplementOf.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
